Feature: Set up demo content

> *As demo person*  
> *I want to have my Jestream site configured for using in the app*  
> *So that I want to use Jestream app with content from the site to demo mobile story*  

<h2>Description</h2> 
To use the data from Jetstream demo instance in the app the instance should be configured properly:
1. Destinations should have nice images and setted up latitude / longitude fields;
2. Item Web API should be configured to allow read access on website for anonymous user.  

To configure the Jetstream site in that way you should simply install "Jetstream mobile app package-1.0.zip" Sitecore package:
